---
title: Pork Schnitzel Banh Mi with Potato Fries & Sriracha Mayo
description: Here’s a fresh new take on everyones favourite Vietnamese sandwich - the Banh Mi! Tender crumbed pork cooked to crunchy perfection is nestled into a toasty wholemeal panini with sriracha mayo, zingy pickled carrots and punchy coriander. Who wants a bite?
